WestLB sets warrants on various German companies . Westdeutsche Landesbank said it has issued 50 million American - style call and put warrants , in 25 equal tranches , on various German companies shares . There are tranches on Bayer AG , BMW AG , Daimler AG , Mannesmann AG , RWE AG , Thyssen AG , VEBA AG , VIAG AG and Volkswagen AG . COMMON TERMS : ONE WARRANT CONTROLS ONE SHARE . EXERCISE PERIOD 12 . DEC . 96 - 05 . DEC . 97 PAYDATE 12 . DEC . 96 LISTING DUSS , FFURT MIN EXER LOT 100 - - Reuter London Newsroom + 44 171 542 7658 
